                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The increase to shield capacity provided by Necramech Redirection is applied after rank bonuses from levelling up the necramech."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Necramech Redirection",
                  "pageId": 1527477,
                  "revisionId": 2686057,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, if a maxed Necramech Redirection is applied to a level 30 Voidrig , the unranked shield capacity (850) is increased by the +200 Base Shield rank bonus, giving 1050. This total is multiplied by 2 (+100% Necramech Redirection shield bonus), giving a grand total of 2100 shield capacity."
